# L1-2: Single PEC reflection wall — infinite-like large wall at x=2
# Validates: |Gamma|^2=1 for both TE/TM, incident angle = reflection angle
# Theory ref: Balanis Ch.5; Born & Wolf 1.5
o wall
v 2.0 -50.0 -50.0
v 2.0 50.0 -50.0
v 2.0 50.0 50.0
v 2.0 -50.0 50.0
vn -1.0 0.0 0.0
f 1//1 2//1 3//1
f 1//1 3//1 4//1
